@startuml UEORMS_State_06
top to bottom direction
hide empty description
title UEORMS State Transition - 6) Inventory and Manufacturing

[*] --> ItemDefined
ItemDefined --> WarehouseMapped : assign warehouse
WarehouseMapped --> StockAvailable : stock posted
StockAvailable --> TransferRequested : request transfer
TransferRequested --> TransferApproved : approve transfer
TransferRequested --> TransferCancelled : cancel transfer
TransferApproved --> StockInTransit : dispatch transfer
StockInTransit --> StockAvailable : receipt confirmed
StockAvailable --> BOMDraft : create BOM
BOMDraft --> BOMReleased : release BOM
BOMReleased --> WorkOrderCreated : create work order
WorkOrderCreated --> OperationsPlanned : define operations
OperationsPlanned --> MaterialsIssued : issue materials
MaterialsIssued --> ProductionCompleted : consume and complete
ProductionCompleted --> InventoryStatsUpdated : update KPIs
InventoryStatsUpdated --> [*]

@enduml
